# Input Echoer Acceptance Test


This is a context step that runs before every scenario

* Open InputEchoer application

## Add Echo Item
* Add text to echo "Hello World"
* Must display "1 echo item"

## Clear Echo Items
* Add text to echo "Hello World"
* Add text to echo "Me Here"
* Add text to echo "You There"
* Add text to echo "Hello Mars"
* Clear echo items
* Must display "0 echo item"